#: ../../../release_details/9.6/maintain-focal-point-in-camera-orientation-widget.md:1
msgid "Maintaining Focal Point Consistency in `vtkCameraOrientationWidget`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/maintain-focal-point-in-camera-orientation-widget.md:3
msgid ""
"The `vtkCameraOrientationWidget` previously called `ResetCamera()` during "
"animation frames and selection actions, which would recalculate the focal "
"point."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/maintain-focal-point-in-camera-orientation-widget.md:5
msgid ""
"This behavior is now controlled by the `ShouldResetCamera` flag. The default "
"value is `True` to preserve existing behavior, but you can set it to `False` "
"to prevent the camera from resetting its focal point during interactions."
msgstr ""
